OL,6,FA father who murdered his two-year-old
OL,7,Fadopted daughter has been sentenced to
OL,8,Flife and must serve at least 23 years
OL,9,Fand six months behind bars.
OL,11,FJan Gholami and his wife Roqia Ghulami
OL,12,Fhave been on trial for the murder of
OL,13,FZahra Ghulami at their Gravesend home
OL,14,Fin May 2020.
OL,16,FDuring the nine-week trial, prosecutor
OL,17,FSally Howes KC said Zahra suffered a
OL,18,Fskull fracture caused by "significant
OL,19,Fimpact with significant energy" at the
OL,20,Fhands of Gholami.
