OL,4,Cgirl jailed for life
OL,6,FThe girl was taken to hospital on 27
OL,7,FMay 2020 and died two days later.
OL,9,FThe prosecution accused the father-of-
OL,10,Ffour of taking out his "bad temper" on
OL,11,Fher and bashing her head against a
OL,12,Fwall.
OL,14,FThe judge, The honourable Mr Justice
OL,15,FWall told Gholami: "You killed a
OL,16,Fdefenceless and vulnerable young child
OL,17,Fin her home.
OL,19,F"It was the culmination of the brutal
OL,20,Fand brutish way you treated the female
OL,21,Fmembers of your family."
