OL,6,FThe court heard his wife was the
OL,7,Fvictim of domestic violence at his
OL,8,Fhands.
OL,10,FShe was also jailed for two years for
OL,11,Fchild cruelty because she "ignored the
OL,12,Fsuffering" of her daughter and failed
OL,13,Fto summon help when she was fatally
OL,14,Finjured.
OL,16,FHis wife Roqia Ghulami was acquitted
OL,17,Fof murder but was found guilty of
OL,18,Fchild neglect and was jailed for two
OL,19,Fyears.
