OL,4,Cgirl jailed for life
OL,6,FFormer farmer Gholami, originally from
OL,7,FAfghanistan, told jurors he went to
OL,8,FTesco that morning, and when he got
OL,9,Fhome, his son said Zahra had fallen
OL,10,Fdown the stairs and was vomiting.
OL,12,FJurors were told Gholami came to the
OL,13,FUK in January 2016 while Ghulami was
OL,14,Fstill in Afghanistan with their
OL,15,Fchildren.
OL,17,FThe couple adopted Zahra in 2017 after
OL,18,FGholami's friend, Zahra's father, felt
OL,19,Funable to look after her following the
OL,20,Fdeath of his wife in childbirth.
