OL,6,FThis happened when Ghulami was in
OL,7,FAfghanistan and the adoption was
OL,8,Fapproved by village elders.
OL,10,FIn January 2019, Gholami applied for
OL,11,Fasylum for Ghulami from the UK, and
OL,12,Fshe arrived with the children to join
OL,13,Fhim.
OL,15,FKent Police's senior investigating
OL,16,Fofficer Det Insp Ross Gurden said:
OL,17,F"Zahra had her life taken away from
OL,18,Fher by two people who had a
OL,19,Fresponsibility to love and care for
OL,20,Fher.
