OL,6,F"Jan inflicted the injuries on Zahra
OL,7,Fwhilst Roqia was completely aware of
OL,8,Fhis behaviour and failed to intervene
OL,9,Fand prevent Zahra from being injured.
OL,11,F"Zahra would have been six now, she
OL,12,Fwould have started school and would be
OL,13,Flearning about the world around her,
OL,14,Fbut instead her young life was cut
OL,15,Fshort through violence inflicted by
OL,16,FJan, who should have been caring for
OL,17,Fher."
